data.description: Welcome to 12002 Ashleigh Park Boulevard, where modern elegance meets suburban comfort! This stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home boasts timeless charm and contemporary features, making it the perfect blend of style and functionality.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warmth of hardwood floors that flow seamlessly throughout the main level. The spacious living area offers plenty of room for relaxation and entertaining, with large windows filling the space with natural light.  On the main level you'll find the  gourmet kitchen, featuring sleek quartz countertops, ample cabinet space, and stainless steel appliances. Whether you're preparing a family meal or hosting a dinner party, this kitchen is sure provide the space you need to create memories.   Upstairs, you'll find the luxurious master suite, complete with a walk-in closet and ensuite bathroom featuring dual vanities and a soaking tub – the perfect retreat after a long day. Three additional bedrooms offer plenty of space for family and guests, with a shared bathroom conveniently located nearby.  Outside, the fenced backyard provides a private oasis for outdoor living, with plenty of space for gardening, play, and relaxation. The attached 2-car garage offers convenience and storage space, while located on a quiet street for enjoyment.   Located in the sought-after community of Ashleigh Park, this home offers easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment, only 20 minutes from downtown Fredericksburg and a minutes drive to the Harrison Crossing shopping center.  Don't miss your chance to make this exquisite property your own – schedule a showing today!
